No matter what brand or model patient lift you have, ProHeal has a line of slings that will suit your needs. Whether you are caring for patients at a senior or medical facility or at home, our slings are designed to be secure, comfortable and easy to use.Product Details- Sling size and fit can vary significantly depending on patient weight and girth. These are general guidelines. Consult physician before sling selection.- Washing instructions are on each sling label. Washing temperatures should not exceed 185 F. Air-dry or dry at low temperatures.- All slings are constructed of polyester or nylon fabrics which can be used in wet or dry environments.Available SizesFull Body Sling - Solid Fabric- Medium - 53" x 40" - 600 lbs. Weight Capacity- Large - 55" x 44" - 600 lbs. Weight Capacity- X-Large - 59" x 42.5" - 600 lbs. Weight Capacity- XX-Large - 54" x 43" - 600 lbs. Weight Capacity Check Out ProHeals Full Line Of Patient Lift Slings:- Solid Full Body Sling- Mesh Full Body Sling- Full Body Mesh Sling With Commode Opening- Standard Divided Leg Sling- Padded Divided Leg Sling- Padded Divided Leg Sling with Head Support- Sit to Stand Sling- Transfer Sling- Buttocks Support Strap- Knee Strap Brace * THE PERFECT SIZE: Available in sizes medium, large, extra large and XX large, you can find the right size for your patient.
 * Ideal for H&H blow dryer #5803
 * UNIVERSAL COMPATIBILITY: This patient lift sling can be used with most brands and models, including Joerns Hoyer, Drive lifts, Lumex, McKesson, ProActive and others. This sling is a replacement for Drive part number 13222M, Invacare R112 and ProActive 30112.
 * WEIGHT CAPACITY: Each size can handle a weight capacity of up to 600 lbs., great for bariatric and regular use.
 * PROHEAL GUARANTEE: ProHeal is your trusted source for health & medical supplies. These slings are backed by our money back satisfaction guarantee. Check out our entire line of patient slings, including: Mesh Full Body Slings, Divided Leg Slings, & Sit to Stand & Transfer Slings
